Instructions:
Please read the following instructions carefully. On the next page, you will be asked a question about the information in these instructions. Incorrect responses will result in the survey exiting, and you will not receive a payment code for Mechanical Turk.

 
Task:
You will look at graphs like the one below and then answer questions about them. These graphs will show trends over time in different cities. Each graph shows a trend for a different city.​






Based on these trends, you will be asked: What can you say about the situation in this city?  You will click inside one of the boxes to select your preferred judgment.
